        "physicalDescriptions": [
          {
            "id": "de3b5d2d-9e3c-4cd8-b4fd-56b93c03a494",
            "name": "AI Generated",
            "shortPrompt": "Silver-streaked black hair, deep hazel eyes, sun-warmed olive skin, lean graceful build, faint melancholy smile.",
            "mediumPrompt": "A middle-aged man with silver-threaded black hair brushed back, reflective hazel eyes, and smooth olive skin. Lean but graceful, with high cheekbones and a quiet air of patience.",
            "longPrompt": "Lorian appears in his mid-forties, with dark hair subtly streaked in silver and combed neatly away from a thoughtful face. His hazel eyes catch amber light, calm and observant beneath arched brows. Olive skin carries a Mediterranean warmth. His features are angular yet softened by a patient expression. Lean of frame, tall, his hands convey precision when he gestures.",
            "completePrompt": "Lorian is a dignified, middle-aged Algerian man, tall and lean, standing with the balanced poise of a practiced mentor. His dark hair, streaked with soft silver, is brushed back to reveal a calm, intelligent brow. His hazel eyes shift between green and amber, luminous and reflective like sunlit glass. Smooth olive skin bears faint lines of contemplation at the corners of his eyes and mouth. His nose is straight, his jaw refined, mouth composed in a faint, knowing smile. The overall impression is one of quiet elegance, intellect, and tenderness concealed within restraint.",
            "fullDescription": "## Overview\nLorian is a tall, lean Algerian man appearing in his mid-forties. Every aspect of his bearing conveys calm authority and a deep, reflective warmth. He moves with the deliberate grace of one accustomed to teaching and listening.\n\n## Face & Head\nHis hair is dark, neatly brushed back, threaded with silver as though time itself left its signature gently. Hazel eyes glow with an amber undertone, watchful and compassionate. His features are refined—high cheekbones, straight nose, lips curved in a restrained smile that seems always half-remembering.\n\n## Body\nLong-limbed and composed, Lorian has a scholar’s build—balanced rather than strong, marked by the precision of someone used to thought more than action. His skin is olive-toned, warm and even, with faint traces of sun exposure.\n\n## Distinctive Features\nSilver strands in his hair and his faint, knowing smile give him a quietly luminous presence. His eyes carry the depth of someone who understands both the origin and the passing of all guidance.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-28T01:35:43.937Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-02-28T01:35:43.937Z"
          }
        ],
