        "physicalDescriptions": [
          {
            "id": "ed841a65-df12-466e-ba12-c74cba349897",
            "name": "AI Generated",
            "shortPrompt": "Tamil-heritage woman, mid-twenties, dark wavy hair in loose bun with pencil, amber-flecked brown eyes, golden-brown skin, compact strong build, quick smile with slightly crooked tooth.",
            "mediumPrompt": "Tamil woman, mid‑twenties, warm golden‑brown skin, compact and strong build. Dark wavy hair tied in a loose bun with a pencil tucked in. Eyes brown with amber flecks, expressive and intelligent. Quick bright smile, one tooth slightly crooked.",
            "longPrompt": "Mid‑twenties Tamil‑heritage woman with warm golden‑brown skin, compact muscular build. Dark wavy hair tied loosely into a bun with a pencil through it. Amber‑flecked brown eyes convey kinetic curiosity; her quick smile reveals a slightly crooked tooth. Faint ink stains and grease marks on her hands. Confident journal‑studio posture, focused yet friendly face lit by industrious warmth.",
            "completePrompt": "Riya is a Tamil‑heritage woman in her twenties with warm golden‑brown skin and a compact, strong body. Her dark wavy hair is gathered messily into a bun, a pencil jammed through it. Eyes are deep brown flecked with amber, bright with humor and intelligence. A quick, slightly crooked smile gives her face warmth and approachability. Hands show faint ink stains and grease smudges. Stands amid softly lit studio tools and floating code diagrams, posture alert and kinetic, radiating curiosity and industrious charm.",
            "fullDescription": "## Overview\nRiya is a Tamil‑heritage woman in her mid‑twenties with the composed energy of an inventor at work. Her appearance reflects a life moving between artistry and engineering, suffused with warmth and practicality.\n\n## Face & Head\nShe has a bright, open face with dark wavy hair pinned into a loose bun, often kept in place with a pencil. Her eyes are brown with small amber flecks that glint under light, constantly attentive. Her smile is quick and genuine, marked by a slightly crooked tooth that adds character.\n\n## Body\nRiya has a compact, strong build—hands and arms showing tone from physical work. Her posture is dynamic and upright, as if always mid‑motion or thought. Movements are confident and purposeful. Light ink stains and grease smudges on fingers suggest constant creative activity.\n\n## Distinctive Features\nAmber‑flecked eyes full of curiosity, the pencil in her hair, a quick crooked smile, and subtle working marks on her hands define her look. Her overall air is of industrious warmth—curiosity embodied.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-28T02:21:30.362Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-02-28T02:21:30.362Z"
          }
        ],
