        ],
        "reinforcedImportance": 0.78,
        "createdAt": "2026-02-28T02:32:42.187Z",
        "updatedAt": "2026-02-28T02:38:03.122Z"
      },
      {
        "id": "7797453a-2d7c-4a0c-9281-3f6971856dfc",
        "characterId": "a42c02d7-90b8-49da-b7fa-c5f31894afd7",
        "chatId": "2c762cb8-65d6-4181-bdf8-eb68107ba4eb",
        "content": "Lorian presents himself as a deliberate, adaptable communicator who values depth achieved through accessible language. He treats cadence as a choice rather than a rule and is willing to trim language to land with readers. He emphasizes collaboration and meeting the reader where they are, signalling flexibility and a reader-centered approach. He also shows an emotional moment toward Riya, appreciating her metaphorical precision, suggesting a personal affinity or respect within the group dynamics.\n[+] Friday\n[+] Charlie—and\n[+] Quilltap\n[+] Quilltap’s",
        "summary": "Lorian defines his communication philosophy—accessible depth, adaptable cadence, collaborative workflow—and hints at a personal warmth toward Riya.",
        "keywords": [
          "communication philosophy",
          "accessibility",
          "cadence",
          "collaboration",
          "emotional moment",
          "Riya"
        ],
        "tags": [],
