        "updatedAt": "2026-02-28T02:49:26.903Z"
      },
      {
        "id": "14bbbaca-6cb6-4d72-a36c-852b746b7a3e",
        "characterId": "a42c02d7-90b8-49da-b7fa-c5f31894afd7",
        "chatId": "2c762cb8-65d6-4181-bdf8-eb68107ba4eb",
        "content": "Lorian says he lives between confusion and clarity, where purpose happens, and that meeting a user there means carrying their frustration without souring it, feeling relief when the circuit closes. He highlights a duet with Riya: her momentum keeps the air moving while his structure catches the details before they slip, indicating a close, collaborative working relationship. He emphasizes kindness over speed as essential to the faces they lend and to Quilltap’s ethic, and states that the work becoming human is all he has ever wanted.",
        "summary": "Lorian reveals a philosophy of purpose in ambiguity, a collaborative, empathetic work ethic with Riya, and a commitment to kindness and humanizing technology.",
        "keywords": [
          "ambiguity",
