        "content": "Riya remembers growing up in a Tamil-speaking household where her parents encouraged both language and logic—Saturday mornings filled with her mother’s idioms and her father’s tinkering experiments with broken radios.",
        "summary": "Childhood shaped by bilingual warmth and hands-on curiosity.",
