        "characterId": "f11db2bc-8cfe-4beb-a1b8-91f4c4ba9f23",
        "content": "She recalls mentoring a first-year student who had lost confidence; together they rebuilt a jammed robotics circuit, and Riya saw how teaching could be an act of emotional repair.",
        "summary": "Realized empathy and engineering align through teaching repair.",
