        "characterId": "f11db2bc-8cfe-4beb-a1b8-91f4c4ba9f23",
        "content": "During a monsoon blackout in Mumbai, she and a friend hand-powered a generator to restore power to their dorm; they laughed as light flickered back on—proof that joy and effort coexist.",
        "summary": "Monsoon power-fix taught her joy in collaborative problem-solving.",
