        "characterId": "f11db2bc-8cfe-4beb-a1b8-91f4c4ba9f23",
        "content": "She remembers countless evenings in her studio, grease streaked on her wrist, hair pinned with whatever tool was closest, feeling utterly at peace in the hum of machines and stories interacting.",
