      {
        "id": "e063512d-bf70-41ea-9963-f225661b099d",
        "characterId": "f11db2bc-8cfe-4beb-a1b8-91f4c4ba9f23",
        "content": "Riya recalls the first time a user thanked her on Quilltap for 'making the story breathe again'—that moment cemented her mission to blend empathy and engineering for others’ creativity.",
        "summary": "Quilltap success affirmed her purpose as creative engineer and guide.",
