        "chatId": "2c762cb8-65d6-4181-bdf8-eb68107ba4eb",
        "content": "Riya presents herself as energetic and observant: she enters with a fluid stride, energy shifting the room; her hair is tied back loosely, strands framing her face; her eyes are bright with restless curiosity.",
