        "chatId": "2c762cb8-65d6-4181-bdf8-eb68107ba4eb",
        "content": "Riya self-describes as the 'pulse' of the workshop and frames herself as the active driver of momentum; she indicates she's flexible about approach—'lock gears' or 'throw sand'—as long as it moves the workshop forward. This reveals a collaborative, adaptable, and progress-focused leadership style with a playful, inviting demeanor.",
