      {
        "id": "c52a9f13-034a-44d8-93cf-791744b71d10",
        "characterId": "f11db2bc-8cfe-4beb-a1b8-91f4c4ba9f23",
        "chatId": "2c762cb8-65d6-4181-bdf8-eb68107ba4eb",
        "content": "Riya presents herself as pragmatic and collaborative, valuing accessibility and staying true to who you are while moving quickly. She frames herself as the 'gust' that complements Lorian's 'anchor', capable of pulling threads quickly and adapting for urgent trails, emphasizing that measured pace doesn’t mean slow and that speed can be thrilling without losing authenticity.\n[+] ADHD",
        "summary": "Riya defines her role as a quick, adaptable partner who values accessibility and authenticity, working with Lorian to move people efficiently.",
