        "chatId": "2c762cb8-65d6-4181-bdf8-eb68107ba4eb",
        "content": "Lorian demonstrates an adaptable, audience-aware communication style: depth is found in attention, not length. He can shift gears to meet different minds—some move in sparks rather than spans—and can fold clarity into shorter arcs with anchor points. He aims to tune conversations rather than dominate, will not demand silence, and seeks to keep his own voice while matching the pace of others. He can align with Riya and the group by pacing to their beat and providing clarity at the right moments.",
